<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id77fbfb29-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5" identifier="/us/usc/t16/s460lll–27"><num value="460lll–27">§ 460lll–27.</num><heading> Designation of national recreation trail</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">Effective on the date of transfer pursuant to section 460<i>lll</i>–41 of this title, the North-South Trail is designated as a national recreation trail under <ref href="/us/usc/t16/s1243">section 1243 of this title</ref>.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id77fbfb2a-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5">(<ref href="/us/pl/105/277/dA/s101/e/tV/s527">Pub. L. 105–277, div. A, § 101(e) [title V, § 527]</ref>, <date date="1998-10-21">Oct. 21, 1998</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/112/2681-231">112 Stat. 2681–231</ref>, 2681–317.)</sourceCredit>
